quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,80,"Alla wa…óanii on e cuu…ói mon …óin ko…óorle, O wa…óani on e guri neemoraa…ói …óin tillisaaji …ói taggoton √Īande eggoton e √Īande ko…ótoton. No e lee…ďi (baali) …óin, e lee…ďi (geloo…ói) …óin e lee…ďi (dammi) …óiin nda…ó…óudi [suudu] e dakmitor…ói haa e saanga."
  16,81,"Alla wa…óanii on e ko o tagi kon …óow…óe. O wa…óani on e pelle …óeen cuu…óor…óe. O wa…óani on comci da…ónday…ói on nguleendi, e conci da…ónday…ói on e hare mon. Ko wano nii o timminirta dokke makko …óeen e dow mon, mbelejo'o on njebbiloto."
  16,82,"Si …ďe nduŇčtiima, anndu ko fawi maa, ko yottingol …ďanngina (pee√Īngol.)"
  16,83,"He…ďe nganndi dokke Alla …óeen; refti …ďe njedda …óe. Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko heefer…ďe."
  16,84,"(JaŇčto) kadi √Īande min immintinoyta e kala mofte seedeejo, refti …ďeen yeddu…ďe sakkitoyantaake (ngantinagol), wanaa kam…ďe ngoni ko …óa…ď…ďiroytee ruttitagol [e yarluyee Joomi ma…ď…ďe]."
  16,85,"Si too√Īu…ďe …ďeen ynj'ii lepte …óeen, …ďe hoynantaake, lepte wanaa …ďe nee…ďnitantee…ďe."
  16,86,"Si sirkoo…ďe …ďeen nji*i kafidaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, …ďe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, ko …óii woni kafidaa…ói amen …ói men ndrewaynoo gah ni ma". [Kafidaa…ói ma…ď…ďe] …óiin njilta e ma…ď…ďe konngol ngol: "Onon ko on fenoo…ďe"."
  16,87,"∆Āe mbernoo e Alla ndeen √Īalnde jebbilaare, kon ko pekindotonoo majjira …ďe."